    "notes": "[l314605] pressing, with Side A stamper from [l313266].\nIssued with 11\" x 22\" foldout lyric/credit/photo insert. Textured cover.\n\nWriting credits taken from insert.\n\nNote that this pressing differs from other Capitol, Jacksonville pressings [r6681095] and [r7435430] in that it uses one stamper from Los Angeles, and another from Jacksonville.\n\nA version with similarly mixed Jacksonville / LA plates, pressed at [l403953] with a different label layout, is here: [r=9886516].",
